00:31:04.000 --> 00:31:06.000
These are the 

00:31:04.000 --> 00:31:06.000
Spanish materials out of which de Falla 

00:31:08.000 --> 00:31:11.000
weaves his colorful, nationalistic 

00:31:11.000 --> 00:31:14.000
tapestry. Here are scenes and dances from 

00:31:14.000 --> 00:31:18.000
